{
  "stem": "21437.8",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At this stage, I mean, you couldn't go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when you asked around-- when I went to Bedzin, as I said, I mean, I was 17 and 1/2.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I really-- you know, I was not 20-odd years old.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I just went there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I just put my feelers out, tentatively.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Nobody knew if there were any list.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "As far as they knew, at the liquidation of the ghetto, they all went to Auschwitz-Treblinka-- Auschwitz-Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This is as far as-- wherever I-- if I-- if I ask this, that was their response.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If you knew somebody has survived, people gravitated, somehow, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the time right after the-- a few months after the war, that you really-- you didn't know much.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, you didn't know where you were going.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You didn't know who is coming.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "People, again, were coming.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And people were going, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you felt this antisemitism.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You felt this resentment.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You felt this-- From who?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Poles, from the Poles, of course.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Bedzin, there were Poles.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the meantime, when the Jews went, the Poles took over.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I couldn't-- I couldn't-- couldn't cope.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Not that I couldn't cope.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I wasn't ready to really-- you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was still hoping and praying.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So it took me a couple of years, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] you know, till I went to-- till I looked-- All together, you know, it took me quite a while before I-- I found my one cousin, Pola.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My cousin, Pola.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in Landsberg--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--in Germany.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think, Landsberg-- wait a second.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If I can spell it-- if I can spell it correctly, I think it would've been, L-A-N-C-B-E-R-G, something like this, you know?",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
